AUXILIARY_DESCRIPTIONS.flatbed trailer: Vehicle used by Abdullah Yusuf to transport 84 illegal aliens near Laredo, Texas, hauling a load from the Auburn Road lot to Dallas, with a forged BOL found in the vehicle and carrying several wooden crates arranged in a rectangle and covered by a tarp. Loaded at the Auburn Road lot, which has no warehouse or loading equipment. A logbook was not found in the vehicle, but a forged BOL was discovered. Stopped by Border Patrol on March 19, 2021, while smuggling aliens.
